{"comments":"NoiseLacunarity - frequency multiplier between octaves in FBM.\n\nRange: 1.0 to finite (clamps at 1.0, no upper bound but must remain finite)\n- **1.0**: No frequency change (all octaves same frequency - not useful)\n- **2.0**: Each octave doubles frequency (standard, natural)\n- **3.0**: Each octave triples frequency (sharper features)\n- **4.0+**: Very rapid frequency increase\n\nControls the \"gap\" between octave frequencies. Standard value is 2.0.\nHigher values create more distinct octave layers.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Material","NoiseLacunarity"],"NoiseLacunarity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[46,56],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Material/NoiseLacunarity.purs","start":[46,1]},"title":"eqNoiseLacunarity"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Material","NoiseLacunarity"],"NoiseLacunarity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[47,58],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Material/NoiseLacunarity.purs","start":[47,1]},"title":"ordNoiseLacunarity"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Material","NoiseLacunarity"],"NoiseLacunarity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[50,43],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Material/NoiseLacunarity.purs","start":[49,1]},"title":"showNoiseLacunarity"}],"comments":"Noise lacunarity (1.0 to finit